<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:15:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于订单和广告收入不断增加，Delivery Hero 上调了收入指引</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/delivery-hero-ups-revenue-guidance-after-q1-beat-2024-04-25/</link><description>德国在线外卖食品公司Delivery Hero周四上调了今年的收入预期，此前该公司公布第一季度增长好于预期，原因是订单和广告收入不断增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/delivery-hero-ups-revenue-guidance-after-q1-beat-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>保乐力加 (Pernod Ricard) 第三季度销售未达预期，预计第四季度充满活力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pernod-ricard-banks-dynamic-q4-after-weaker-than-expected-q3-sales-2024-04-25/</link><description>法国烈酒集团保乐力加(Pernod Ricard)周四公布第三季度销售额弱于预期，其主要市场中国和美国仍面临巨大压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pernod-ricard-banks-dynamic-q4-after-weaker-than-expected-q3-sales-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>独家：卫星图像显示，中国停泊与朝俄武器转让有关的船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-harbors-ship-tied-north-korea-russia-arms-transfers-satellite-images-show-2024-04-25/</link><description>路透社获得的卫星图像显示，随着美国对北京支持莫斯科乌克兰战争的担忧日益加剧，中国正在为一艘受美国制裁的俄罗斯货船提供停泊地，这艘货船涉及朝鲜向俄罗斯转让武器。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-harbors-ship-tied-north-korea-russia-arms-transfers-satellite-images-show-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯程序员玩“猫捉老鼠”游戏智取审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-programmers-play-cat-mouse-game-outsmart-censors-2024-04-25/</link><description>安东尼·鲁德科夫斯基 (Antony Rudkovsky) 15 岁左右时，他开始自学如何构建虚拟专用网络 (VPN) 来访问俄罗斯无法访问的互联网内容。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:08:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-programmers-play-cat-mouse-game-outsmart-censors-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>丰田与腾讯合作吸引中国年轻司机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/toyota-says-partner-with-tencent-china-2024-04-25/</link><description>丰田汽车周四表示，将与中国游戏和社交媒体领导者腾讯在中国合作，这家日本汽车制造商旨在满足年轻消费者对技术增强型汽车的品味。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 04:40:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/toyota-says-partner-with-tencent-china-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国坚持经济数据，称国防支出“透明”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-stands-by-economic-data-says-defence-spending-transparent-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国为其经济数据的真实性进行了辩护，并声称其军费开支“透明合理”，同时驳斥了美国印太司令部司令本周发表的“典型的双重标准”言论。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 04:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-stands-by-economic-data-says-defence-spending-transparent-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，苹果一季度出货量下降6.6%，失去中国市场第一宝座</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-loses-top-spot-china-market-with-shipments-down-66-q1-data-shows-2024-04-25/</link><description>研究公司 IDC 周四的初步数据显示，由于激烈的竞争，苹果公司在 2024 年第一季度失去了中国最大智能手机销售商的桂冠，因为其智能手机出货量同比下降 6.6%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 04:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-loses-top-spot-china-market-with-shipments-down-66-q1-data-shows-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯-奔驰将为中国市场推出豪华电动货车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-launch-luxury-electric-van-chinese-market-2024-04-25/</link><description>梅赛德斯-奔驰货车部门负责人告诉德国杂志《WirtschaftsWoche》，梅赛德斯-奔驰计划在其 VAN.EA 平台上为中国市场推出一款豪华电动货车。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 04:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-launch-luxury-electric-van-chinese-market-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>小鹏汽车CEO称软件、AI升级进入“超快周期”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-ceo-says-its-software-ai-upgrades-enter-super-fast-cycle-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国电动汽车(EV)制造商小鹏汽车周四表示，其软件和人工智能培训升级将从5月份开始进入“超快周期”，并希望其平台的使用范围将扩大到其他亚洲国家和欧洲。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 03:55:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-ceo-says-its-software-ai-upgrades-enter-super-fast-cycle-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车初创公司蔚来为新版ET7轿车设定起价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-startup-nio-sets-starting-price-new-version-et7-sedan-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国电动汽车 (EV) 初创公司 Nio 首席执行官周四表示，已将新版 ET7 轿车的起价定为 428,000 元人民币（59,063 美元）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-startup-nio-sets-starting-price-new-version-et7-sedan-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪推出阳王品牌第三款超豪华车型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-unveils-third-ultra-luxury-model-under-yangwang-brand-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪周四推出了阳王品牌的第三款超豪华车型U7，在价格战愈演愈烈的情况下，该公司进军高端市场以提高盈利能力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-unveils-third-ultra-luxury-model-under-yangwang-brand-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>台湾候任总统表示，中国应该有信心与我们对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-elect-appoints-new-team-says-islands-security-difficult-2024-04-25/</link><description>当选总统赖清德周四在任命新的国家安全和外交团队时表示，中国应该有信心与台湾合法选举的政府进行对话，他称这是前所未有的挑战。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:45:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-elect-appoints-new-team-says-islands-security-difficult-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>日产、马自达为中国推出新车型，力求卷土重来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-unveils-four-concept-cars-fuel-china-comeback-2024-04-25/</link><description>日产汽车和马自达汽车周四推出了专为中国驾驶者量身定制的新车，这标志着日本汽车制造商重新努力在全球最大的汽车市场重新占据一席之地。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:37:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-unveils-four-concept-cars-fuel-china-comeback-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>股市受科技股下滑打击；日元在干预区震荡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-25/</link><description>亚洲股市周四下跌，Facebook 母公司 Meta Platforms 令人失望的盈利预测重创科技股，而日元兑美元自 1990 年以来首次跌破 155 美元，引发了东京干预的担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:32:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>小米SU7汽车订单锁定超7.5万辆 6月交付目标超万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-locks-over-75000-orders-su7-car-targets-over-10000-deliveries-june-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国智能手机制造商小米创始人雷军周四表示，截至 4 月 24 日，其运动型 SU7 电动轿车已锁定 75,723 辆订单，并计划在 6 月份交付超过 10,000 辆。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:19:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-locks-over-75000-orders-su7-car-targets-over-10000-deliveries-june-2024-04-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>